<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一大早，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比拉着菲利斯的头发，叫她起床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“起床！”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里是新家，没有仆人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们起来给妈妈一个惊喜吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们来打扫房子，准备早餐吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我已经叫醒彼得了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩儿们穿好衣服，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后生起了炉子，烧上了水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们摆好了桌子，但是找不到合适的盘子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，她们把盐放在烟灰缸里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把面包放在烤盘里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>做完这些以后，她们和彼得一起来到外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>房子在山坡上，孩子们可以看到很远的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山脚下有一条铁路和一条隧道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里比我们伦敦的家好看多了。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车站太远了，看不到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去下面看火车吧。”彼得建议说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在这里也能看到。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们坐一会儿吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是他们三个人坐在一块大石头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当妈妈八点钟找他们的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们已经在阳光下睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们早上生了炉子，烧了水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是妈妈起床时，炉子已经灭了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水烧干了，水壶也烧焦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系。我都准备好了。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我找到一个昨天我们没发现的小房间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走进厨房旁边的小房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>桌子上有维尼夫人留下来的烤牛肉、面包、黄油、奶酪和苹果派。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早餐苹果派！”彼得高兴地大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，妈妈和孩子们打开行李，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>开始整理他们的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了快傍晚，妈妈说：“今天就干到这儿吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚餐之前我得休息一个小时。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163546</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们互相看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们做什么呢？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然她已经知道了答案。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去铁路边吧！”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山脚下有一个木栏杆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们翻了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看到了铁路，包括闪光的铁道、电线杆和信号灯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，孩子们听到轰隆隆的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196075</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一辆火车从隧道里开了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>轨道上的石头都跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”鲍比慢慢地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它就像一条巨龙经过，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>用它火热的翅膀扇动着我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。没想到可以离火车这么近，太棒了！”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不知道这辆火车是不是开往伦敦的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸在那里。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去看看吧！”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们往火车站跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们沿着铁路走，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>数着电线杆，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后跳到站台上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车站的一边有一大堆煤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>煤堆后面有一条白线。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得问站台工作人员，这个白线是做什么用的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是为了显示有多少煤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样，如果有人偷煤，我们就会知道！”工作人员笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得觉得他很友好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们离开时，一想到很快就会回来，就非常兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>